						"subtitle": "Extending Cloudflare security to all your networks",
						"copy": "When organizations need to protect their networks, IT departments typically turn to legacy hardware boxes or cloud 'scrubbing' providers. But traditional solutions just aren't designed to fulfill the Internet's basic needs: security, performance, and reliability.<br><br>Magic Transit delivers network functions at Cloudflare scale— that's DDoS protection, traffic acceleration, and much more from every Cloudflare data center— for on-premise, cloud-hosted, and hybrid networks.\n\n![magic-transit-hero-illustration](//cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/slt3lc6tev37/7Ggp3F8tlOOMMPmCfR863A/0521926f7b3d6b2569406218ba224a2e/magic-transit-hero-illustration.svg)",
